# Incubyte project context

Salary Management MVP: replace ACME HR spreadsheets for ~10k employees.

## Doc order (on conflict)

1. `docs/scope.md` — boundary
2. `docs/requirements.md` — FR/NFR tests
3. `docs/spec.md` — implementation + status table
4. `docs/erd.md` — schema

Also read `AGENTS.md` at repo root.

## Stack

- `api/`: Bun.serve + bun:sqlite + bun test. No Express, no better-sqlite3.
- `web/`: Vite + React + Vitest. Do not switch to Bun HTML imports.
- Root: `bun install`, `bun run dev|test|lint|build|seed`.

## Domain

- Integer minor units for money; no floats.
- Direct component edits in MVP — no audit log, no change reason.
- Analytics USD conversion via `fx_rates` only; never mutate native stored amounts.
- Component types from `salary_component_definitions` (runtime extensible).

## Not in MVP

Audit, approvals, RBAC, compensation events, CSV I/O, live FX, effective-dated history.

Update `docs/spec.md` Implementation Status when completing a feature area.
